                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-10-15</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">一张简简单单的纸带出了整个中华文化的脉络，和世界人类的走向。装帧插图妥妥的满分。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1083847217">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1083847217" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1083847217" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1083847217">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/123508360/">泛不系之舟</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-09-12</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">版面设计非常漂亮，是很多学者文章的合辑，内容很涨知识，只是错别字有点多，扣一星</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
        <p>&gt; <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/20456359/comments/">更多短评 46 条</a></p>
