  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7345842/" class="title-link">闲读之书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7345842"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/zuoyefeng/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u29146210-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zuoyefeng/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">歐陽喵</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-01-16"
      class="main-meta">2015-01-16 23:02:37</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7345842_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  可闲读以广见闻。装帧有特色，用纸考究，内容偏散，本身各部分都是大学问大手艺，故此书自然不能一一而及。插图风格雅致有趣，然而一些手工工序过于简略，大抵知者能悟，不知者固茫然——传统的手艺不是本来就是如此么？

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7345842_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7345842_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





